OL,4,G0010F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GParamedics treat a woman whose
OL,6,     Gdefibrillator inside her chest
OL,7,     Ghas delivered an electric shock
OL,8,     Gto her heart, and a man who's had
OL,9,     Gbowel surgery who thinks he may
OL,10,     Ghave an infection.
